Nell Hudson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nell_Hudson 0 Nell Rose Hudson is an English actress best known for her recurring role as Laoghaire MacKenzie in the Starz television drama series Outlander. In 2016 and 2017, she portrayed the role of Mrs Skerrett in the ITV period drama series Victoria.
